WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 7=

00:01:31.210 --> 00:01:33.410
(Hope you won't regret your decision)

00:01:43.620 --> 00:01:45.690
What've you been up to lately,
Teacher Li?

00:01:49.300 --> 00:01:50.460
Just busy with random stuff.

00:01:51.180 --> 00:01:52.020
Oh.

00:01:52.380 --> 00:01:53.460
- You...
- You...

00:01:54.930 --> 00:01:55.820
You go first.

00:01:57.260 --> 00:01:58.540
How've you been lately?

00:02:00.020 --> 00:02:00.860
I'm good.

00:02:01.330 --> 00:02:02.170
You...

00:02:02.570 --> 00:02:03.620
How are you guys doing?

00:02:05.490 --> 00:02:06.490
All doing fine.

00:02:07.460 --> 00:02:08.380
Oh, that's nice.

00:02:08.450 --> 00:02:09.340
- Then...
- Oh right.

00:02:11.340 --> 00:02:12.260
This is for you.

00:02:12.540 --> 00:02:14.340
Use this card for coffee from now on.

00:02:15.690 --> 00:02:16.660
This...

00:02:17.010 --> 00:02:18.260
Is this okay?

00:02:19.260 --> 00:02:20.380
Don't be so polite.

00:02:22.290 --> 00:02:24.610
I've been wanting to thank you

00:02:24.660 --> 00:02:25.610
for that day.

00:02:26.820 --> 00:02:27.660
But...

00:02:27.670 --> 00:02:28.570
I get it.

00:02:29.170 --> 00:02:30.170
It's fine.

00:02:31.100 --> 00:02:32.060
Thanks.

00:02:35.060 --> 00:02:36.890
Bring your favorite girl next time.

00:02:37.170 --> 00:02:38.410
Favorite girl?

00:02:40.730 --> 00:02:42.730
Hope I run into her at your café.

00:02:43.260 --> 00:02:44.450
Thanks again.

00:02:48.570 --> 00:02:50.010
I saw your latest work.

00:02:50.340 --> 00:02:51.180
Mm?

00:02:52.170 --> 00:02:54.340
Ximei married Prince Beiye,
a human prince.

00:02:54.690 --> 00:02:56.570
She never cared for grand castles.

00:02:56.570 --> 00:02:57.780
Or endless wealth.

00:02:57.780 --> 00:02:59.570
Because the prince was kind and gentle,

00:02:59.780 --> 00:03:01.610
a rare soul in this world,

00:03:01.780 --> 00:03:03.940
she fought to be worthy of him.

00:03:04.130 --> 00:03:06.820
Willing to lose all her memories for it.

00:03:07.130 --> 00:03:10.260
She renounced her demon identity.

00:03:10.410 --> 00:03:11.890
She once believed

00:03:12.010 --> 00:03:13.500
she truly loved

00:03:13.500 --> 00:03:14.690
this prince who brought her light.

00:03:15.690 --> 00:03:17.850
But the uncontrollable longing
in her heart

00:03:18.100 --> 00:03:20.340
quietly awakened her sealed memories.

00:03:21.340 --> 00:03:23.720
At night, when she turned into a demon,
she deeply loved

00:03:23.890 --> 00:03:25.780
Shou Gongyuan, the demon realm envoy.

00:03:26.100 --> 00:03:26.940
How is it?

00:03:27.260 --> 00:03:28.170
Good?

00:03:31.450 --> 00:03:34.100
I got a bit reckless while writing.

00:03:34.540 --> 00:03:35.540
Hope you don't mind.

00:03:36.570 --> 00:03:37.410
What happens next?

00:03:37.610 --> 00:03:38.660
I don't know.

00:03:39.940 --> 00:03:41.170
I was wondering

00:03:41.450 --> 00:03:43.220
can I fulfill myself through the story?

00:03:44.170 --> 00:03:45.100
What do you think?

00:03:49.220 --> 00:03:50.130
As long as you like it.

00:03:55.940 --> 00:03:57.130
But stories...

00:03:57.730 --> 00:03:59.170
are still just stories.

00:04:04.980 --> 00:04:05.820
Mm.

00:04:06.660 --> 00:04:07.500
Exactly.

00:04:18.750 --> 00:04:19.740
Look at the craftsmanship.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:20.940
It's really well made.

00:04:22.050 --> 00:04:23.460
And there's a small pouch inside.

00:04:24.050 --> 00:04:24.910
Oh.

00:04:24.930 --> 00:04:25.770
Okay.

00:04:26.340 --> 00:04:27.180
This one?

00:04:36.140 --> 00:04:36.980
Hey.

00:04:40.140 --> 00:04:40.980
Hey.

00:04:42.900 --> 00:04:44.930
Whose little cutie are you?

00:04:44.930 --> 00:04:45.770
Huh?

00:04:46.220 --> 00:04:47.220
Where's your mom?

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:48.410
How can you be this cute?

00:04:48.410 --> 00:04:49.340
Mm? So cute.

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:50.580
Even if you're this cute,

00:04:50.590 --> 00:04:52.050
I still have to take you
to find your mom.

00:04:52.050 --> 00:04:53.660
Got it?

00:04:57.370 --> 00:04:58.220
Find what?

00:05:00.980 --> 00:05:02.050
This is your son.

00:05:03.170 --> 00:05:04.020
Do you like him?

00:05:06.140 --> 00:05:06.980
Ah.

00:05:07.220 --> 00:05:08.850
This dog's practically a genius.

00:05:18.170 --> 00:05:19.050
Honey.

00:05:21.370 --> 00:05:22.410
Done washing already?

00:05:22.700 --> 00:05:23.540
Almost.

00:05:25.100 --> 00:05:25.940
How about

00:05:26.250 --> 00:05:28.290
we find time these two days
to check out dogs?

00:05:31.100 --> 00:05:32.050
You wanna get a dog?

00:05:32.700 --> 00:05:34.490
Didn't we agree before the wedding?

00:05:35.370 --> 00:05:37.980
French Bulldog or Corgi, your choice.

00:05:38.290 --> 00:05:39.170
Alright.

00:05:39.850 --> 00:05:40.980
Get whatever.

00:05:42.100 --> 00:05:43.140
It's up to you.

00:05:43.260 --> 00:05:44.410
No need to discuss it with me.

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:48.580
Why do you act like this
whenever I mention dogs?

00:05:49.290 --> 00:05:50.170
What's my problem?

00:05:50.170 --> 00:05:51.460
I'm not stopping you.

00:05:52.290 --> 00:05:53.460
But let's be clear first.

00:05:53.700 --> 00:05:55.220
If you get a dog, you take care of it.

00:05:55.220 --> 00:05:56.140
I'm not helping.

00:05:57.490 --> 00:05:58.730
Fine, fine.

00:05:58.900 --> 00:06:00.460
Forget it, no dog then.

00:06:01.140 --> 00:06:03.050
Every time I bring up dogs,
you get this attitude.

00:06:03.300 --> 00:06:05.100
I really don't get
what dogs ever did to you.

00:06:05.460 --> 00:06:07.540
Do you think this is the right time
to get a dog?

00:06:07.700 --> 00:06:09.460
Dogs are pets. They need affection.

00:06:09.580 --> 00:06:10.900
It takes time and energy.

00:06:11.020 --> 00:06:12.580
It's no different from raising a child.

00:06:12.730 --> 00:06:13.930
We're so busy with work

00:06:13.940 --> 00:06:15.290
and have tons of
stuff to handle.

00:06:15.290 --> 00:06:16.980
When would we have time for a dog?

00:06:17.170 --> 00:06:18.370
Yes, you're busy.

00:06:18.660 --> 00:06:19.700
Who isn't?

00:06:19.700 --> 00:06:20.850
Everyone around us has a dog.

00:06:20.850 --> 00:06:21.810
Only you're too busy.

00:06:21.810 --> 00:06:23.050
Even celebrities have dogs.

00:06:23.290 --> 00:06:25.900
Do you even compare to celebrities?

00:06:26.810 --> 00:06:27.730
To put it bluntly.

00:06:27.900 --> 00:06:29.930
I'm not wasting my time on a dog.

00:06:30.170 --> 00:06:32.100
With that time,
I could be advancing my career.

00:06:32.410 --> 00:06:33.930
Right, only you're ambitious.

00:06:33.930 --> 00:06:35.020
You're always right.

00:06:35.020 --> 00:06:36.140
I can't control others.

00:06:36.290 --> 00:06:37.410
I can't even change

00:06:37.410 --> 00:06:38.540
the person next to me.

00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:40.180
I just focus on myself.

00:06:40.250 --> 00:06:41.730
I focus on improving myself.

00:06:41.850 --> 00:06:43.220
I'll do my best, that's enough.

00:06:44.610 --> 00:06:45.720
And you, as a man,

00:06:45.930 --> 00:06:47.410
can't you think more maturely?

00:06:47.540 --> 00:06:48.980
Stop being so impulsive, okay?

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.490
Let me tell you this one last time!

00:06:50.830 --> 00:06:52.290
I hate it when you call me immature.

00:06:52.510 --> 00:06:54.340
Didn't we agree to get a dog
when we got married?

00:06:54.410 --> 00:06:55.900
You know how much I love dogs!

00:06:55.900 --> 00:06:57.250
A lot was agreed on before marriage.

00:06:57.490 --> 00:06:58.730
We said we'd travel once a year.

00:06:58.730 --> 00:06:59.570
Did we ever?

00:06:59.810 --> 00:07:01.100
You said you'd surprise me on

00:07:01.100 --> 00:07:03.100
anniversaries and Valentine's Day.
Did you?

00:07:03.100 --> 00:07:04.050
Why bring up travel now?

00:07:04.050 --> 00:07:05.220
When would we have time?

00:07:05.220 --> 00:07:06.730
Didn't I get you gifts? I did.

00:07:06.730 --> 00:07:08.410
You said you didn't like it.
You said it yourself!

00:07:08.410 --> 00:07:09.280
- Sorry!
- Called me wasteful.

00:07:09.310 --> 00:07:11.410
It's my fault, all my fault.

00:07:11.410 --> 00:07:13.850
I'm the one
who's kept this family poor, okay?

00:07:13.850 --> 00:07:15.100
It's always about money.

00:07:15.100 --> 00:07:16.220
I'm not a wealthy heir!

00:07:16.370 --> 00:07:17.410
Haven't I worked hard?

00:07:17.410 --> 00:07:18.780
Making money takes time.
Haven't I tried?

00:07:18.780 --> 00:07:20.780
Have you ever made any money? Have you?

00:07:21.100 --> 00:07:23.340
Aren't I the one
managing everything in this household?

00:07:23.340 --> 00:07:26.370
I told you to teach kids piano
in small classes.

00:07:26.370 --> 00:07:27.250
You kept making excuses.

00:07:27.250 --> 00:07:28.780
Kept writing things nobody buys.

00:07:28.780 --> 00:07:30.460
Songs that nobody wants, right?

00:07:30.460 --> 00:07:32.220
I'm just garbage to you!

00:07:32.220 --> 00:07:33.580
Do you regret marrying me?

00:07:33.630 --> 00:07:35.140
You wish you'd found someone rich, huh?

00:07:35.140 --> 00:07:36.250
Like Pianpian's husband, right?

00:07:36.700 --> 00:07:38.610
Hua's rich, go to him.

00:07:38.610 --> 00:07:40.140
Your mom likes him a lot,
so hurry and go!

00:07:40.660 --> 00:07:42.700
Go! Go find Hua!

00:07:43.780 --> 00:07:45.220
You jerk!

00:08:21.610 --> 00:08:22.490
I'm sorry.

00:08:54.770 --> 00:08:56.610
I couldn't give you the life you wanted.

00:09:00.060 --> 00:09:02.010
And I dragged you into my childish mess.

00:09:05.490 --> 00:09:06.420
I'm sorry.

00:09:08.940 --> 00:09:09.940
If I'd known

00:09:10.180 --> 00:09:11.730
it would end up like this,

00:09:14.580 --> 00:09:15.820
I never would've gotten married.

00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:19.820
Never would've dragged you down.

00:09:23.250 --> 00:09:24.610
I can't give you what you want.

00:09:28.010 --> 00:09:30.180
Now I don't even know who I am.

00:09:32.610 --> 00:09:33.580
Yu.

00:09:37.010 --> 00:09:38.460
I can't keep up with you.

00:09:40.300 --> 00:09:41.420
I'm sorry.

00:09:46.010 --> 00:09:48.340
I know I've been tiring you out.

00:09:50.220 --> 00:09:52.300
I'm so done with this life. Mortgage,

00:09:52.300 --> 00:09:53.700
utilities, gas bills
every month,

00:09:53.700 --> 00:09:56.300
and then hesitating
over a decent outfit.

00:09:58.340 --> 00:10:00.610
I'm scared my colleagues
and friends will notice

00:10:00.610 --> 00:10:03.490
I wear the same two or three bags
over and over.

00:10:04.650 --> 00:10:07.610
I'm even more scared
when my parents ask about your salary

00:10:07.940 --> 00:10:08.820
I'd have to lie again.

00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:11.490
I have to lie and say Xiu earns well.

00:10:11.610 --> 00:10:13.770
And that I'm living happily.

00:10:17.820 --> 00:10:19.300
You should tell them the truth.

00:10:22.890 --> 00:10:23.940
I know.

00:10:26.130 --> 00:10:27.460
They look down on me.

00:10:28.100 --> 00:10:29.060
They think I'm poor.

00:10:31.490 --> 00:10:32.340
I love you.

00:10:36.460 --> 00:10:39.820
I won't let anyone look down on you.

00:10:43.720 --> 00:10:44.770
Have you ever regretted it?

00:10:47.420 --> 00:10:49.490
(Back then, between love and money.)

00:10:51.060 --> 00:10:52.650
(I didn't hesitate for a second.)

00:10:54.220 --> 00:10:56.060
(I thought money didn't matter.)

00:10:57.340 --> 00:10:59.250
(Love was the only thing
that truly counted.)

00:11:02.350 --> 00:11:03.340
(I thought you'd be the one)

00:11:03.340 --> 00:11:05.420
(to make money with me.)

00:11:07.340 --> 00:11:08.940
(And I always believed)

00:11:09.820 --> 00:11:10.890
(that you're the one.)

00:11:11.580 --> 00:11:12.650
(Right?)

00:11:13.980 --> 00:11:16.180
(Sometimes I feel like
we're from two different planets)

00:11:18.010 --> 00:11:19.370
(When I step into your world,)

00:11:20.340 --> 00:11:22.100
(I'm under ten times the gravity.)

00:11:23.800 --> 00:11:25.530
(And I can hardly breathe
from the lack of oxygen)

00:11:32.220 --> 00:11:34.340
Remember how long
it's been since we watched a movie?

00:11:39.100 --> 00:11:40.010
No.

00:11:46.490 --> 00:11:47.420
Me neither.

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:55.730
(I'll never mention
getting a dog again.)

00:11:56.730 --> 00:11:58.340
(And I won't hang out with my friends.)

00:11:59.850 --> 00:12:01.650
(I can do all the things I don't like.)

00:12:02.650 --> 00:12:04.340
(Work as hard as you do.)

00:12:05.550 --> 00:12:07.250
(Try to become the person
you hoped I'd be)

00:12:08.610 --> 00:12:09.580
(Because I love you.)

00:12:12.300 --> 00:12:13.940
This dog food's been
selling well lately.

00:12:13.940 --> 00:12:14.940
Take some to try.

00:12:15.580 --> 00:12:17.340
Sure, I'll get this one.

00:12:17.700 --> 00:12:19.060
- Okay.
- Two bags.

00:12:19.060 --> 00:12:19.900
Okay.

00:12:20.610 --> 00:12:22.460
Total's 1,116 yuan.

00:12:22.460 --> 00:12:23.820
I'll take 1,000 yuan.

00:12:24.100 --> 00:12:25.370
And I'll throw in two cans for you.

00:12:25.850 --> 00:12:27.010
You're too kind, Sir.

00:12:27.010 --> 00:12:27.850
Thanks a lot.

00:12:27.940 --> 00:12:29.460
Come on, we're old friends.

00:12:29.460 --> 00:12:30.700
Thanks for supporting my business.

00:12:30.920 --> 00:12:31.770
Come back anytime.

00:12:31.770 --> 00:12:32.610
Sure.

00:12:35.650 --> 00:12:36.490
Here, take this.

00:12:38.580 --> 00:12:39.420
Let's go.

00:12:41.060 --> 00:12:42.580
- Bye.
- Take care.

00:12:46.100 --> 00:12:48.420
You seem pretty close with
that pet shop owner.

00:12:48.940 --> 00:12:51.060
Not really,
the shop's just near my place.

00:12:51.150 --> 00:12:52.730
I go there to
play with the dogs sometimes.

00:12:55.850 --> 00:12:56.940
No dog at home.

00:12:57.820 --> 00:12:58.850
Then go out and play with them.

00:13:00.250 --> 00:13:01.220
Now you've got one.

00:13:03.220 --> 00:13:04.070
Eh.

00:13:04.100 --> 00:13:05.510
Why suddenly want a dog?

00:13:05.510 --> 00:13:06.460
But you don't like dogs.

00:13:07.370 --> 00:13:08.700
But you do.

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:12.120
Besides, some people
write about it in songs.

00:13:12.960 --> 00:13:15.890
"You said you wanted a gentle hound."

00:13:16.460 --> 00:13:18.770
"To help me find my long-lost freedom."

00:13:20.940 --> 00:13:22.020
I'm giving you freedom.

00:13:22.460 --> 00:13:23.300
Don't you want it?

00:13:26.640 --> 00:13:28.180
I asked Pianpian to take a look for me.

00:13:28.660 --> 00:13:29.820
She said it's a purebred.

00:13:30.700 --> 00:13:32.260
Her family's got tons of cats and dogs.

00:13:32.580 --> 00:13:33.460
She really knows her stuff.

00:13:35.780 --> 00:13:36.620
Yeah?

00:13:36.900 --> 00:13:37.900
What are you smiling at?

00:13:38.500 --> 00:13:39.340
Nothing.

00:13:40.380 --> 00:13:42.460
I just feel like
something I've dreamed of

00:13:43.020 --> 00:13:44.500
is just someone else's daily life.

00:13:44.980 --> 00:13:47.620
Yeah, like how she
got a new sports car today.

00:13:47.900 --> 00:13:48.820
Jealous?

00:13:49.060 --> 00:13:50.140
Why would I be jealous?

00:13:50.860 --> 00:13:53.060
As a woman, I'm no worse than her.

00:13:53.820 --> 00:13:55.460
One day, I'll surpass her.

00:13:57.220 --> 00:13:58.620
Then I wish you success.

00:14:03.180 --> 00:14:04.580
Why not we?

00:14:05.020 --> 00:14:06.420
Cars don't really interest me.

00:14:13.300 --> 00:14:14.980
Then what does catch your interest?

00:14:16.380 --> 00:14:17.700
I'm into…

00:14:21.580 --> 00:14:23.220
(Gong)

00:14:23.540 --> 00:14:24.420
Xiaoxi,

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.220
don't you think that, in this car,

00:14:26.220 --> 00:14:27.500
we're like a family of three?

00:14:27.820 --> 00:14:29.540
A silly son sitting in the back.

00:14:31.220 --> 00:14:32.820
We're educated people.

00:14:33.220 --> 00:14:35.340
Stop making weird family jokes.

00:14:37.020 --> 00:14:38.020
Besides,

00:14:39.660 --> 00:14:41.420
even if we were a family of three,

00:14:42.260 --> 00:14:43.900
we make a better couple, don't we?

00:14:44.660 --> 00:14:45.620
Hey, Gong Buhui.

00:14:45.940 --> 00:14:47.700
Do you flirt with everyone?

00:14:47.820 --> 00:14:49.180
You have no sense of humor.

00:14:50.300 --> 00:14:51.660
Zhazha Xiu's calling.

00:14:55.580 --> 00:14:56.420
Hello.

00:14:56.580 --> 00:14:57.420
Hey, Gong.

00:14:57.980 --> 00:14:59.820
Why aren't you answering my call?

00:14:59.940 --> 00:15:02.140
Tell me. Got another pup now?

00:15:02.700 --> 00:15:03.540
Yeah.

00:15:03.860 --> 00:15:04.700
Whoa.

00:15:05.020 --> 00:15:05.980
That's blunt.

00:15:05.990 --> 00:15:07.060
I don't know how to respond.

00:15:07.340 --> 00:15:08.180
What's the matter?

00:15:08.580 --> 00:15:10.220
Tightwad Sen's treating us to Linglong.

00:15:10.500 --> 00:15:11.340
Can you believe it?

00:15:11.820 --> 00:15:12.660
Tonight.

00:15:13.300 --> 00:15:14.580
I might not make it tonight.

00:15:14.820 --> 00:15:16.260
Speak clearly.

00:15:16.500 --> 00:15:18.420
All that stuttering. So unlike me.

00:15:19.300 --> 00:15:20.140
Go.

00:15:25.180 --> 00:15:27.020
Well? Are you going or not?

00:15:27.300 --> 00:15:29.340
We're waiting for your answer, hurry up.

00:15:32.340 --> 00:15:33.260
Okay.

00:15:36.420 --> 00:15:37.460
What's going on with Xiu?

00:15:38.180 --> 00:15:39.740
No idea, he's mumbling.

00:15:39.740 --> 00:15:40.900
Probably busy.

00:15:42.780 --> 00:15:44.300
If he's busy, tell him not to come.

00:15:45.270 --> 00:15:46.740
Then tell Luanluan not to come either.

00:15:47.740 --> 00:15:48.580
Too late.

00:15:56.740 --> 00:15:58.660
I'll head out first.
Be careful going home.

00:15:58.820 --> 00:15:59.660
Mm.

00:16:00.620 --> 00:16:01.460
Xiu.

00:16:06.260 --> 00:16:07.580
You never thought about

00:16:09.060 --> 00:16:10.180
bringing me along?

00:16:19.100 --> 00:16:23.220
(Xiuluo)

00:16:23.420 --> 00:16:24.420
(Linglong)
Yo, yo.

00:16:24.740 --> 00:16:25.740
Little fairy.

00:16:26.020 --> 00:16:27.260
Why are you here so early?

00:16:27.660 --> 00:16:28.660
Missed me already?

00:16:28.980 --> 00:16:30.180
I did, I missed you so much.

00:16:30.180 --> 00:16:31.020
Come give me a hug.

00:16:31.340 --> 00:16:32.580
I really missed you.

00:16:33.180 --> 00:16:34.140
Knew it.

00:16:34.620 --> 00:16:35.660
Give it to me.

00:16:36.060 --> 00:16:37.580
- Come here.
- Luanluan.

00:16:37.910 --> 00:16:38.780
Hello.

00:16:38.820 --> 00:16:39.660
Hello.

00:16:40.060 --> 00:16:41.580
Didn't Xiu come with you?

00:16:42.060 --> 00:16:44.060
He'll be here soon, don't worry.

00:16:44.340 --> 00:16:45.180
What about Sen?

00:16:45.230 --> 00:16:46.500
He's already in the private room.

00:16:46.860 --> 00:16:48.780
I came out to wait for you.

00:16:49.620 --> 00:16:51.140
Oh, waiting for us?

00:16:54.420 --> 00:16:55.740
Why'd you bring Bowie today?

00:16:56.180 --> 00:16:57.180
When you called me,

00:16:57.180 --> 00:16:59.380
I happened to be getting it groomed
at the pet salon,

00:16:59.380 --> 00:17:00.500
so I just brought it along.

00:17:01.140 --> 00:17:03.140
Besides, Xiu mentioned
missing it last time.

00:17:03.140 --> 00:17:04.300
Haven't seen it in ages.

00:17:04.300 --> 00:17:05.140
Give me a kiss!

00:17:10.420 --> 00:17:12.620
Are you trying to get me drunk tonight?

00:17:12.620 --> 00:17:13.580
Girl.

00:17:23.500 --> 00:17:24.980
What are you doing?

00:17:28.860 --> 00:17:29.700
Sen.

00:17:30.100 --> 00:17:31.500
Hey, Bei.

00:17:31.540 --> 00:17:32.380
You guys came so early.

00:17:32.540 --> 00:17:33.580
I haven't ordered yet.

00:17:34.180 --> 00:17:35.300
Cut the act.

00:17:35.700 --> 00:17:37.620
You can't even read the menu, can you?

00:17:38.260 --> 00:17:39.660
Do you think you're funny?

00:17:39.900 --> 00:17:41.180
You look hilarious yourself.

00:17:41.580 --> 00:17:42.420
Bei.

00:17:42.900 --> 00:17:44.180
Why'd you bring it along too?

00:17:44.500 --> 00:17:46.060
Didn't you say to call everyone?

00:17:46.140 --> 00:17:47.060
So I called it too.

00:17:47.400 --> 00:17:48.340
You call that a person?

00:17:48.980 --> 00:17:49.980
Halfway.

00:17:51.900 --> 00:17:52.740
Gong.

00:17:52.860 --> 00:17:53.860
You sit there.

00:17:54.140 --> 00:17:55.300
Think you're all mysterious?

00:17:55.540 --> 00:17:58.060
I just don't wanna
look at your ugly face.

00:17:58.500 --> 00:17:59.940
Is it your birthday today?

00:18:00.380 --> 00:18:02.500
I didn't bring a gift. Annoyed yet?

00:18:02.500 --> 00:18:04.420
Are you stupid?

00:18:04.620 --> 00:18:06.300
Don't you know when my birthday is?

00:18:06.660 --> 00:18:08.500
Speaking of birthdays makes me mad.

00:18:08.700 --> 00:18:10.780
This guy gave me a kids' smart watch

00:18:11.060 --> 00:18:13.660
for my birthday two years ago.

00:18:14.000 --> 00:18:14.840
What was that mean?

00:18:14.850 --> 00:18:16.030
You don't get it?

00:18:16.340 --> 00:18:18.580
- Afraid you'd lose your way in love.
- How sweet.

00:18:18.580 --> 00:18:19.660
And last year,

00:18:19.780 --> 00:18:21.540
you gave me a Xinhua Dictionary.

00:18:21.620 --> 00:18:22.620
How do you explain that?

00:18:22.660 --> 00:18:24.740
Still afraid you'll get lost
and can't read the signs.

00:18:24.860 --> 00:18:26.020
Dear.

00:18:26.620 --> 00:18:27.980
Can we just make him disappear?

00:18:27.980 --> 00:18:29.420
That was my wish when I turned eighteen.

00:18:29.420 --> 00:18:30.580
Still hasn't come true.

00:18:30.580 --> 00:18:31.580
From now on,

00:18:31.740 --> 00:18:33.140
that's my wish too.

00:18:35.430 --> 00:18:36.860
Wait, I'm gonna buy some cigarettes.

00:18:37.540 --> 00:18:39.540
Ah, I want some throat lozenges.

00:18:39.820 --> 00:18:40.660
I'll buy it for you.

00:18:40.780 --> 00:18:42.300
Do you know what flavor I like?

00:18:43.100 --> 00:18:44.220
Let's go together.

00:18:46.580 --> 00:18:52.540
(Yang Huo Xiao Zhen
Imported Life Supermarket)

00:18:52.540 --> 00:18:54.100
Sake Jelly, Wasabi Shrimp.

00:18:54.200 --> 00:18:55.740
Cheesy Fried Noodles,
Spicy Clam Pancake.

00:18:55.920 --> 00:18:56.980
Tied in Love, Served with Carp.

00:18:57.100 --> 00:18:58.020
Illegal PDA Bites.

00:18:58.980 --> 00:18:59.820
The Old Drunk's Intent.

00:18:59.820 --> 00:19:00.900
Three-Treasure Braised Chicken.

00:19:02.380 --> 00:19:03.540
Alright, that's enough.

00:19:03.700 --> 00:19:04.660
I still want dumplings.

00:19:04.660 --> 00:19:05.700
That's enough.

00:19:06.340 --> 00:19:07.660
Ladies, anything else you want?

00:19:07.660 --> 00:19:08.500
Order whatever.

00:19:08.900 --> 00:19:10.020
A four-jin lobster.

00:19:10.100 --> 00:19:10.980
Keep your mouth shut.

00:19:10.980 --> 00:19:12.740
Oyster Crispy Bun.

00:19:12.740 --> 00:19:13.580
Xiu loves that.

00:19:13.860 --> 00:19:14.900
Got it, that's all. Thanks.

00:19:14.900 --> 00:19:15.980
Add one more.

00:19:15.980 --> 00:19:16.940
Stop, can we even finish?

00:19:16.940 --> 00:19:17.780
I can finish it.

00:19:18.000 --> 00:19:19.900
- Hey, can we really finish this?
- What's wrong?

00:19:20.780 --> 00:19:21.820
You're so stingy.

00:19:23.260 --> 00:19:24.100
Eh.

00:19:24.860 --> 00:19:25.700
Eh.

00:19:26.460 --> 00:19:28.580
What's that?
Haven't seen you wear it before.

00:19:29.780 --> 00:19:30.620
A seal.

00:19:30.820 --> 00:19:32.540
A seal. Who gave it to you?

00:19:32.540 --> 00:19:33.380
Xiu gave it to me.

00:19:34.060 --> 00:19:35.340
Xiu did.

00:19:36.100 --> 00:19:37.900
Looks like there's something
engraved on it.

00:19:37.980 --> 00:19:39.580
He carved it himself. "Drunk".

00:19:39.860 --> 00:19:41.300
I always thought Sen was stingy.

00:19:41.300 --> 00:19:44.100
Never expected Xiu to give
such cheap stuff too.

00:19:44.980 --> 00:19:45.820
Pour it yourself.

00:19:46.700 --> 00:19:48.740
♪Our treasure♪

00:19:49.020 --> 00:19:51.540
♪Just a metal pendant♪

00:19:51.700 --> 00:19:53.820
♪A sentiment that never fades♪

00:19:53.820 --> 00:19:55.980
♪Yet my love for you isn't fully done♪

00:19:56.220 --> 00:20:00.490
♪But loving you could never tire me♪

00:20:00.500 --> 00:20:01.900
♪My dear♪

00:20:02.180 --> 00:20:03.020
Have a seat.

00:20:03.820 --> 00:20:04.660
You're one to talk.

00:20:04.660 --> 00:20:05.660
What would you give?

00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:07.620
A kids' watch? A dictionary?

00:20:15.060 --> 00:20:15.900
My heart.

00:20:16.220 --> 00:20:17.380
That's so cringy.

00:20:19.300 --> 00:20:20.140
Thanks.

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:21.010
He's crazy.

00:20:21.030 --> 00:20:22.020
Sit closer.

00:20:26.300 --> 00:20:27.140
This one.

00:20:28.310 --> 00:20:29.820
Why are you coming with me
all of a sudden?

00:20:30.180 --> 00:20:31.260
You don't want me to go?

00:20:32.290 --> 00:20:33.140
Not that.

00:20:33.140 --> 00:20:34.420
Thought you weren't into them.

00:20:34.740 --> 00:20:36.060
Do they not like me?

00:20:36.700 --> 00:20:37.540
No way.

00:20:37.620 --> 00:20:38.860
Then why can't I go?

00:20:40.780 --> 00:20:42.500
Sir, have you decided on the cigarettes?

00:20:43.220 --> 00:20:44.060
No.

00:20:44.980 --> 00:20:46.300
Smoke less.

00:20:46.300 --> 00:20:47.660
No time, hurry up.

00:20:48.700 --> 00:20:52.660
♪In my world, cloudy days are you.
Sunny days are you♪

00:20:52.660 --> 00:20:54.900
♪Even rainy days are you♪

00:20:54.900 --> 00:21:00.740
♪In my world, the sun and moon are you.
The stars are you♪

00:21:01.140 --> 00:21:03.420
♪In my world, the mountains are you♪

00:21:03.420 --> 00:21:08.060
♪The rivers are you,
and every view is you♪

00:21:08.060 --> 00:21:13.340
♪Every moment of my future
is all about you♪

00:21:13.340 --> 00:21:14.740
Smoke less.

00:21:14.740 --> 00:21:16.260
No time, hurry up.

00:21:31.140 --> 00:21:32.380
Something just came up.

00:21:33.180 --> 00:21:34.420
I have to go.

00:21:34.420 --> 00:21:35.580
You guys carry on.

00:21:38.380 --> 00:21:39.940
Hey, what's going on, Luanluan?

00:21:45.180 --> 00:21:46.100
Why are you leaving?

00:21:47.340 --> 00:21:48.300
Don't be like this.

00:21:48.740 --> 00:21:49.660
Stop talking nonsense.

00:21:53.140 --> 00:21:53.980
Sit down.

00:21:56.800 --> 00:21:57.900
I don't care about anything else.

00:21:58.260 --> 00:22:00.260
We agreed to sing
and eat together tonight.

00:22:00.940 --> 00:22:01.780
You showed up first.

00:22:02.070 --> 00:22:03.460
You can't just leave for no reason.

00:22:07.100 --> 00:22:08.140
What's going on here?

00:22:10.340 --> 00:22:11.700
Guess Xiu's planning to bring...

00:22:12.460 --> 00:22:13.740
First come, first served.

00:22:15.580 --> 00:22:17.020
But I'm the one who came later.

00:22:20.780 --> 00:22:22.380
You're the friend.

00:22:22.380 --> 00:22:24.380
And you're the karaoke king.

00:22:24.380 --> 00:22:29.340
Which means you can't leave.

00:22:30.220 --> 00:22:32.700
Who'll sing if you go?

00:22:33.260 --> 00:22:34.700
I'll queue up your signature song.

00:22:34.700 --> 00:22:35.540
Just wait a sec.

00:22:47.700 --> 00:22:49.100
Hi, can we serve the food now?

00:22:51.060 --> 00:22:51.900
Sure.

00:23:07.140 --> 00:23:08.380
I saw you come in with a woman.

00:23:08.400 --> 00:23:09.780
- Which woman?
- Where's she hiding?

00:23:09.790 --> 00:23:10.780
- What woman?
- Where is she?

00:23:10.940 --> 00:23:11.780
Wh…

00:23:12.140 --> 00:23:13.700
Tell me, where's the woman?

00:23:13.780 --> 00:23:15.340
There is no woman.

00:23:15.500 --> 00:23:17.180
I clearly saw you come with her.

00:23:17.500 --> 00:23:18.940
(No one likes acting.)

00:23:20.620 --> 00:23:21.900
(I've played countless roles.)

00:23:21.980 --> 00:23:23.260
(All to fight evil with evil.)

00:23:24.020 --> 00:23:25.980
(Help those women escape tragedy.)

00:23:26.980 --> 00:23:28.420
(Ironically.)

00:23:28.740 --> 00:23:29.780
(One's stance)

00:23:29.780 --> 00:23:31.900
(can shift with emotions and interests.)

00:23:33.960 --> 00:23:35.460
(I never thought I'd end up on the side)

00:23:35.580 --> 00:23:36.700
(of those I once condemned.)

00:23:36.860 --> 00:23:38.740
(Offering her comfort
and encouragement.)

00:23:40.660 --> 00:23:42.180
(I hid among the accomplices.)

00:23:42.180 --> 00:23:43.180
(To the woman betrayed.)

00:23:43.280 --> 00:23:44.580
(The one who deserves sympathy.)

00:23:44.700 --> 00:23:46.340
(I'll put on a shameless performance.)

00:23:49.780 --> 00:23:51.060
(Today, I play the traitor.)

00:23:51.580 --> 00:23:52.620
(I'm sorry.)

00:24:41.740 --> 00:24:43.020
Sorry, I'm late.

00:24:50.980 --> 00:24:52.580
Hey, look who's here.

00:24:52.740 --> 00:24:55.300
Xiu, you brought such a beautiful girl.

00:24:55.500 --> 00:24:57.020
Won't your wife get mad?

00:24:57.940 --> 00:24:59.900
Gong has a bad memory, huh?

00:25:00.150 --> 00:25:01.460
It's been ages since we last met.

00:25:01.780 --> 00:25:03.420
Have you all forgotten

00:25:03.420 --> 00:25:04.700
who his real wife is?

00:25:07.180 --> 00:25:08.180
Long time no see.

00:25:16.260 --> 00:25:17.180
Welcome.

00:25:17.380 --> 00:25:18.580
Didn't expect Sister Yu to come.

00:25:18.740 --> 00:25:20.100
I told you not to call me "Sister".

00:25:20.420 --> 00:25:21.340
Am I that old?

00:25:21.760 --> 00:25:22.610
Sorry.

00:25:22.630 --> 00:25:23.900
Got too excited. My mistake.

00:25:23.980 --> 00:25:26.220
Yeah, we all used to
call you Yu back then.

00:25:26.420 --> 00:25:27.460
Bei's got quite the memory.

00:25:27.700 --> 00:25:29.820
Xiu used to call me that every day.

00:25:29.840 --> 00:25:30.900
And you just followed along.

00:25:31.060 --> 00:25:33.420
But it sounds cringy now.

00:25:33.580 --> 00:25:34.780
- Have a seat.
- Okay.

00:25:35.860 --> 00:25:37.140
My girlfriend sits here.

00:25:37.540 --> 00:25:38.500
You sit there.

00:25:39.060 --> 00:25:40.300
Sit here.

00:25:40.820 --> 00:25:42.060
Alright, don't move.

00:25:43.290 --> 00:25:44.180
You sit inside.

00:25:44.180 --> 00:25:45.500
I like being closer to the door.

00:25:51.300 --> 00:25:52.860
Don't just stare. Let's eat.

00:25:53.020 --> 00:25:54.300
- Food will get cold soon.
- Ah.

00:25:54.400 --> 00:25:55.580
Here, let me pour you some wine.

00:25:55.580 --> 00:25:56.860
Let's drink together, come on.

00:25:57.550 --> 00:25:58.540
Yu, come on.

00:25:58.580 --> 00:26:00.660
Oh, I don't drink. Let Xiu join you.

00:26:00.740 --> 00:26:01.820
Hey, Xiu.

00:26:07.500 --> 00:26:08.380
Come on.

00:26:09.700 --> 00:26:11.260
Let's drink together, come on.

00:26:11.540 --> 00:26:12.740
Let's toast. Quick.

00:26:13.900 --> 00:26:15.020
Come on.

00:26:15.850 --> 00:26:16.700
Welcome.

00:26:16.740 --> 00:26:17.940
Welcome.

00:26:25.140 --> 00:26:26.340
Yu, you got a dog?

00:26:28.100 --> 00:26:29.220
Xiu, didn't you say...

00:26:30.700 --> 00:26:32.820
Didn't you say
having a dog costs too much?

00:26:33.540 --> 00:26:34.460
Cost too much?

00:26:35.860 --> 00:26:38.340
Yet he bought me a bag
worth tens of thousands.

00:26:38.620 --> 00:26:39.700
He didn't even blink.

00:26:39.980 --> 00:26:41.300
So how could a dog be too pricey?

00:26:41.300 --> 00:26:43.020
- Really?
- It's just that before,

00:26:43.300 --> 00:26:45.180
I was too busy with work
to take care of one.

00:26:45.580 --> 00:26:47.780
Now business is good and I have time,

00:26:48.180 --> 00:26:49.340
so I bought it for him.

00:26:53.140 --> 00:26:53.980
Oh.

00:26:54.140 --> 00:26:55.060
Hey, cutie.

00:26:55.220 --> 00:26:56.100
Be careful.

00:26:56.220 --> 00:26:57.220
Got it.

00:26:58.100 --> 00:26:58.940
Here, have this.

00:26:59.460 --> 00:27:00.460
Thanks.

00:27:08.340 --> 00:27:09.660
What's that saying again?

00:27:11.300 --> 00:27:12.380
"A virtuous wife at home

00:27:12.380 --> 00:27:13.900
lets the husband fool around
without worry."

00:27:14.300 --> 00:27:15.660
Men won't do reckless things.

00:27:18.060 --> 00:27:20.700
Now Xiu's so career-driven.

00:27:20.700 --> 00:27:21.940
Because Yu's been guiding him well.

00:27:22.100 --> 00:27:23.180
Not at all.

00:27:23.580 --> 00:27:24.820
It's all his own hard work.

00:27:25.140 --> 00:27:26.420
And also

00:27:26.830 --> 00:27:28.180
he's lucky to have many benefactors.

00:27:37.020 --> 00:27:39.100
What are you scared of? So cowardly.

00:27:43.380 --> 00:27:44.420
We're old friends.

00:27:44.420 --> 00:27:45.980
Thanks for supporting my business.

00:27:45.980 --> 00:27:47.220
Come back anytime.

00:27:48.840 --> 00:27:50.220
This dog is so well cared for.

00:27:50.390 --> 00:27:51.260
Whose is it?

00:27:51.300 --> 00:27:52.220
Mine.

00:27:55.260 --> 00:27:56.140
It's mine.

00:28:08.820 --> 00:28:10.140
Must be troublesome to raise?

00:28:10.780 --> 00:28:11.700
It's alright.

00:28:12.260 --> 00:28:13.140
Got used to it.

00:28:13.780 --> 00:28:14.780
After all, I like it.

00:28:18.900 --> 00:28:20.140
I was wondering why Xiu's

00:28:20.340 --> 00:28:21.500
always running out.

00:28:21.940 --> 00:28:23.340
I thought he was just into drinking,

00:28:23.520 --> 00:28:25.020
but turns out he's here
playing with dogs.

00:28:28.220 --> 00:28:29.540
No need to run out anymore.

00:28:30.900 --> 00:28:32.220
Your Xiu

00:28:32.240 --> 00:28:33.230
likes hanging out with us.

00:28:33.230 --> 00:28:34.620
Not sure what he sees in it.

00:28:35.380 --> 00:28:37.700
But he doesn't like playing at home.

00:28:38.140 --> 00:28:39.260
Is it because this little cutie

00:28:39.260 --> 00:28:40.500
bites too much?

00:28:43.740 --> 00:28:44.860
Did it bite you?

00:28:50.300 --> 00:28:51.620
I noticed these two beauties

00:28:51.620 --> 00:28:53.060
as soon as I came in.

00:28:54.260 --> 00:28:55.260
Why not introduce them?

00:28:55.260 --> 00:28:56.180
Whose girlfriends are they?

00:28:56.180 --> 00:28:57.020
Right.

00:28:57.100 --> 00:28:57.980
Then let's introduce.

00:28:58.380 --> 00:29:00.500
This is my girlfriend, Li Xiaoxi.

00:29:01.260 --> 00:29:02.180
And this is Yu.

00:29:02.540 --> 00:29:03.380
Hi.

00:29:04.120 --> 00:29:05.700
I've heard them talk about you so much.

00:29:05.780 --> 00:29:07.260
I was wondering when we'd meet.

00:29:07.670 --> 00:29:08.870
Didn't expect it to be this soon.

00:29:08.880 --> 00:29:10.580
If they mention me,
it's never in a good way.

00:29:10.700 --> 00:29:11.720
How could they?

00:29:12.120 --> 00:29:13.340
If they dared to badmouth you,

00:29:13.460 --> 00:29:14.660
Xiu would lose his temper.

00:29:15.300 --> 00:29:16.180
Really?

00:29:16.220 --> 00:29:17.140
Of course.

00:29:18.140 --> 00:29:19.650
Bei, the catch,

00:29:19.660 --> 00:29:21.660
finally has a girlfriend.

00:29:22.180 --> 00:29:23.540
After being single for years.

00:29:23.860 --> 00:29:25.300
Turns out you were waiting for her.

00:29:26.460 --> 00:29:28.180
Li Xiaoxi is stunning.

00:29:28.190 --> 00:29:29.180
And sharp with words.

00:29:29.300 --> 00:29:30.750
Perfect match.

00:29:34.940 --> 00:29:35.900
What happened?

00:29:38.660 --> 00:29:40.060
I think some dog fur got in my throat.

00:29:40.540 --> 00:29:41.940
Sorry. You guys keep talking.

00:29:46.540 --> 00:29:47.380
And…

00:29:47.400 --> 00:29:48.420
What about this beauty here?

00:29:49.300 --> 00:29:50.460
Who's your boyfriend?

00:29:51.100 --> 00:29:52.020
Her name's Luanluan.

00:29:53.220 --> 00:29:54.100
She...

00:29:57.220 --> 00:29:58.740
She's actually your husband's lover.

00:29:59.820 --> 00:30:01.100
Hey, are you out of your mind?

00:30:15.980 --> 00:30:17.020
Why're you so worked up?

00:30:17.020 --> 00:30:18.100
I… I'm not… I...

00:30:18.800 --> 00:30:19.700
You don't really think

00:30:19.740 --> 00:30:21.340
I'd believe anything Gong says?

00:30:21.600 --> 00:30:22.740
It's not like I just met him.

00:30:22.980 --> 00:30:24.900
Exactly, Yu knows me best.

00:30:28.580 --> 00:30:29.500
Besides,

00:30:30.220 --> 00:30:31.940
she's young and gorgeous.

00:30:32.220 --> 00:30:33.580
She could get any man she wants.

00:30:34.110 --> 00:30:35.460
Why would she cling to a married guy?

00:30:36.500 --> 00:30:38.340
Who'd stoop to something so low?

00:30:41.060 --> 00:30:42.260
Exactly.

00:30:43.020 --> 00:30:45.100
She's got really high standards.

00:30:45.100 --> 00:30:46.340
She didn't even give me a chance.

00:30:46.900 --> 00:30:48.460
She's got a boyfriend now.

00:30:49.220 --> 00:30:50.900
Her boyfriend is

00:30:51.300 --> 00:30:53.420
kinda ugly, a bit sneaky,

00:30:53.430 --> 00:30:54.940
eats like a piglet,

00:30:55.140 --> 00:30:56.100
and selfish,

00:30:56.500 --> 00:30:58.380
but what can I say? That's love.

00:30:58.660 --> 00:30:59.980
Everyone's got their own taste.

00:31:00.840 --> 00:31:01.900
She's just into this guy.

00:31:04.800 --> 00:31:06.100
Luanluan, he just dissed your boyfriend

00:31:06.180 --> 00:31:07.340
and you're not mad?

00:31:08.100 --> 00:31:09.740
If he dared to talk about Xiu like that,

00:31:10.260 --> 00:31:11.660
I'd lose it on him right there.

00:31:12.380 --> 00:31:13.220
No, I wouldn't dare.

00:31:13.660 --> 00:31:14.820
He's joking.

00:31:15.310 --> 00:31:16.540
My boyfriend's really great.

00:31:17.140 --> 00:31:17.980
Really?

00:31:18.740 --> 00:31:21.020
Bring him out next time
so we can all hang out.

00:31:21.340 --> 00:31:22.940
Our treat, okay?

00:31:23.460 --> 00:31:24.300
Okay.

00:31:24.380 --> 00:31:25.300
Sure.

00:31:30.300 --> 00:31:33.300
Yu, I heard you work in fashion design.

00:31:33.820 --> 00:31:35.500
Where can I buy your designs?

00:31:35.820 --> 00:31:37.940
I rushed out today
and didn't prepare anything.

00:31:37.940 --> 00:31:40.180
Next time, I'll bring you
some outfits as gifts.

00:31:41.340 --> 00:31:42.500
Li Xiaoxi, what do you do?

00:31:42.980 --> 00:31:43.900
I run a flower shop.

00:31:44.200 --> 00:31:45.300
At Renmin Road Intersection.

00:31:45.940 --> 00:31:46.780
Called Liang.

00:31:47.380 --> 00:31:48.300
Liang.

00:31:48.900 --> 00:31:50.300
Oh, I know that place.

00:31:50.300 --> 00:31:51.780
My friend ordered flowers there before.

00:31:52.500 --> 00:31:53.580
Hey, Xiu.

00:31:53.860 --> 00:31:55.620
From now on, for Valentine's Day

00:31:55.700 --> 00:31:57.700
and for our anniversaries
or any special days,

00:31:58.000 --> 00:31:59.820
you can't order flowers for me
from anywhere else.

00:31:59.820 --> 00:32:00.940
Got it? Hmm.

00:32:03.980 --> 00:32:04.820
Luanluan.

00:32:05.620 --> 00:32:06.580
What do you do?

00:32:07.180 --> 00:32:08.100
I'm an actress.

00:32:08.580 --> 00:32:09.420
A stage actress.

00:32:10.100 --> 00:32:11.340
An actress.

00:32:12.980 --> 00:32:14.500
Hope I get to see your performance.

00:32:15.780 --> 00:32:16.620
Sure.

00:32:21.300 --> 00:32:24.180
Come on, let's all toast.

00:32:24.180 --> 00:32:25.100
- Come on.
- Come on.

00:32:42.340 --> 00:32:43.780
(Everyone here knows)

00:32:44.180 --> 00:32:45.540
(we're all just acting.)

00:32:46.380 --> 00:32:48.500
(But no one wants to call it out.)

00:32:49.180 --> 00:32:50.860
(Because no one's really lying.)

00:32:51.580 --> 00:32:53.100
(We wear our masks of pretense.)

00:32:53.340 --> 00:32:55.820
(Yet what we perform
is our truest selves.)

00:32:56.500 --> 00:32:59.500
(What an absurd game adults play.)

00:33:22.300 --> 00:33:24.380
Tiger Tiger, Bug. One to zero.

00:33:24.380 --> 00:33:25.500
Tiger Tiger, Tiger.

00:33:25.500 --> 00:33:26.380
Two to zero.

00:33:26.380 --> 00:33:27.750
Tiger Tiger, Chicken.

00:33:27.750 --> 00:33:28.620
Two to one.

00:33:28.620 --> 00:33:30.340
Tiger Tiger, Chicken.

00:33:30.700 --> 00:33:32.100
How long have you two been together?

00:33:32.580 --> 00:33:33.420
Tiger Tiger.

00:33:33.580 --> 00:33:34.620
Huh...

00:33:34.660 --> 00:33:35.500
Who?

00:33:35.820 --> 00:33:37.620
About four months now, right?

00:33:37.900 --> 00:33:38.900
132 days.

00:33:41.820 --> 00:33:43.260
Any plans to marry?

00:33:45.420 --> 00:33:47.260
Ah, I'm in no hurry.

00:33:47.380 --> 00:33:48.940
I still want my future wife

00:33:49.000 --> 00:33:50.060
to get to know me better.

00:33:51.140 --> 00:33:51.980
Fair enough.

00:33:52.200 --> 00:33:53.620
She might not want to marry
once she knows.

00:33:54.150 --> 00:33:55.220
Go play now.

00:33:55.980 --> 00:33:58.260
Why stress about marriage?

00:33:58.580 --> 00:34:00.940
Dating longer isn't bad at all.

00:34:03.140 --> 00:34:04.020
True.

00:34:04.640 --> 00:34:05.820
In case, right after marriage,

00:34:06.340 --> 00:34:08.060
you start wanting to date again.

00:34:11.580 --> 00:34:12.580
Here you go.

00:34:13.260 --> 00:34:15.100
Once married, you can't date anymore?

00:34:19.380 --> 00:34:20.220
You can.

00:34:21.700 --> 00:34:24.100
But it's a whole different world.

00:34:25.940 --> 00:34:26.900
For example...

00:34:27.940 --> 00:34:29.380
Back before we got married,

00:34:30.180 --> 00:34:31.500
whenever I craved something,

00:34:32.140 --> 00:34:33.740
Xiu would cook it for me himself,

00:34:34.180 --> 00:34:36.380
drive halfway across the city
to bring it to me,

00:34:36.620 --> 00:34:38.540
and it'd still be hot when he got there.

00:34:39.660 --> 00:34:40.700
After we got married,

00:34:41.060 --> 00:34:42.660
I'd often cook a whole table of dishes.

00:34:42.940 --> 00:34:44.340
Saying he'd be home for dinner.

00:34:44.860 --> 00:34:45.860
But the food gets cold

00:34:46.300 --> 00:34:47.380
and he's still not there.

00:34:49.500 --> 00:34:51.220
Maybe we've both just been too busy.

00:34:57.940 --> 00:34:58.780
Mm?

00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:03.500
You won't make me wait for you
to come home

00:35:03.500 --> 00:35:04.580
for dinner every day, will you?

00:35:04.800 --> 00:35:07.060
No way. If anyone's waiting,
it'll be me waiting for you.

00:35:07.060 --> 00:35:09.460
Besides, I actually enjoy cooking.

00:35:09.460 --> 00:35:10.380
You won't get the chance.

00:35:11.700 --> 00:35:13.420
What else don't I know about you?

00:35:13.420 --> 00:35:14.340
Hey, hey.

00:35:14.860 --> 00:35:16.660
Can you two be considerate of

00:35:17.020 --> 00:35:18.780
the single people here?

00:35:19.420 --> 00:35:20.420
Single people.

00:35:21.180 --> 00:35:22.380
That doesn't include me.

00:35:23.900 --> 00:35:24.940
I've got a girlfriend.

00:35:25.260 --> 00:35:26.100
Who is she?

00:35:26.660 --> 00:35:28.380
Da Ji, Diao Chan, or Yang Yuhuan?

00:35:28.900 --> 00:35:30.220
I'm serious.

00:35:32.260 --> 00:35:33.540
Let me make it official.

00:35:34.660 --> 00:35:37.260
I've been chasing her for seven years.

00:35:37.620 --> 00:35:38.460
And now we're

00:35:38.740 --> 00:35:41.300
officially together!

00:35:42.880 --> 00:35:43.740
Thanks.

00:35:43.740 --> 00:35:45.220
Thank you.

00:35:45.340 --> 00:35:46.660
We'll take your word for it.

00:35:47.100 --> 00:35:49.620
As your friends,
let us give you some advice.

00:35:49.780 --> 00:35:50.620
You cool with that?

00:35:50.650 --> 00:35:52.380
If it doesn't work out,
don't waste her time.

00:35:52.500 --> 00:35:53.340
Come on,

00:35:53.740 --> 00:35:55.060
I'll show you her photo.

00:35:55.600 --> 00:35:56.710
- I show them first.
- Pretty?

00:35:56.710 --> 00:35:57.560
- Pretty.
- Let me see.

00:35:57.580 --> 00:35:58.500
Yu, take a look.

00:35:59.260 --> 00:36:00.100
Pretty?

00:36:00.220 --> 00:36:01.400
Hey, it really is.

00:36:01.400 --> 00:36:02.260
Do we match?

00:36:02.300 --> 00:36:03.980
So do all the girls in your group

00:36:03.980 --> 00:36:05.340
have to be pretty?

00:36:06.100 --> 00:36:07.380
Then you have to come more often.

00:36:08.100 --> 00:36:09.780
I'm worried I might get in your way.

00:36:12.820 --> 00:36:14.100
Congrats.

00:36:18.620 --> 00:36:21.500
This person in the photo looks kinda...

00:36:22.300 --> 00:36:23.380
I think I've seen her before.

00:36:25.140 --> 00:36:25.980
Where?

00:36:26.340 --> 00:36:27.380
At my shop.

00:36:28.540 --> 00:36:30.140
Remember? You mentioned...

00:36:30.420 --> 00:36:31.780
That cute one with the bob haircut.

00:36:32.260 --> 00:36:34.780
Oh right, yeah! The super adorable one.

00:36:35.260 --> 00:36:36.140
Hey, hold on.

00:36:37.100 --> 00:36:37.940
You guys...

00:36:38.260 --> 00:36:39.940
You already knew about
the two of them...

00:36:43.140 --> 00:36:44.340
Oh my goodness.

00:36:45.780 --> 00:36:48.180
I feel like a clueless little fool.

00:36:49.300 --> 00:36:51.220
Don't you feel even a twinge of guilt?

00:36:53.100 --> 00:36:54.700
Gong, come on, hey.

00:36:55.220 --> 00:36:57.100
Look, I've chased her for years.

00:36:57.380 --> 00:36:58.740
Got mocked in all kinds of ways.

00:36:59.500 --> 00:37:00.340
Like...

00:37:00.500 --> 00:37:01.660
"Let me see your backup number."

00:37:01.660 --> 00:37:03.100
"Three digits?"

00:37:03.340 --> 00:37:04.580
Also, "if you and

00:37:04.580 --> 00:37:06.020
her dog fell into the water,

00:37:06.260 --> 00:37:07.380
who would she save first?"

00:37:07.980 --> 00:37:09.740
Questions like that.

00:37:10.740 --> 00:37:12.300
You know I'm overly sensitive.

00:37:12.860 --> 00:37:14.580
I know you'd roast me nonstop.

00:37:14.700 --> 00:37:16.380
Thinking of me like this
breaks my heart.

00:37:17.380 --> 00:37:19.100
Turns out you never understood me.

00:37:19.940 --> 00:37:20.940
You found the person

00:37:20.940 --> 00:37:22.260
who matters most in your life.

00:37:22.700 --> 00:37:24.260
Do you even realize how lucky you are?

00:37:25.340 --> 00:37:26.620
I should be happy for you.

00:37:26.740 --> 00:37:27.580
Come on.

00:37:27.900 --> 00:37:30.620
You probably just think
I'm a fool with a crush.

00:37:31.660 --> 00:37:32.740
I don't think that.

00:37:34.020 --> 00:37:35.540
I love you, and you love me.

00:37:35.860 --> 00:37:36.820
That's luck.

00:37:38.670 --> 00:37:40.340
If you don't love me,
I won't love you back.

00:37:40.340 --> 00:37:41.420
That's self-interest.

00:37:42.340 --> 00:37:44.260
If you don't love me
but I still love you,

00:37:44.900 --> 00:37:45.940
that's what love really is.

00:37:54.660 --> 00:37:56.260
Didn't expect you to be like this, Gong.

00:37:56.840 --> 00:37:58.660
If I'd known earlier,
I wouldn't have kept it from you.

00:38:00.340 --> 00:38:02.460
So hurry up and learn to swim.

00:38:02.940 --> 00:38:04.180
I bet she'll save the dog first.

00:38:04.190 --> 00:38:05.080
Shut up already.

00:38:05.080 --> 00:38:07.500
Do you ever say anything nice?

00:38:09.220 --> 00:38:10.180
Wait, Sen,

00:38:11.780 --> 00:38:14.140
how did she suddenly say yes to you?

00:38:16.940 --> 00:38:18.100
I chased her for seven years.

00:38:18.980 --> 00:38:19.820
Seven years.

00:38:20.000 --> 00:38:21.260
Even a glacier would've melted by now.

00:38:21.540 --> 00:38:22.820
Let me drop a fact.

00:38:23.140 --> 00:38:25.420
A glacier won't melt in seven years.

00:38:27.820 --> 00:38:28.700
Come on, have a seat.

00:38:29.900 --> 00:38:30.740
Here.

00:38:34.100 --> 00:38:36.140
As your older brother,
let me give you some advice.

00:38:37.220 --> 00:38:39.700
You don't really know her that well yet.

00:38:40.230 --> 00:38:41.660
I think you should hold back a little.

00:38:44.060 --> 00:38:45.420
Why should he hold back?

00:38:46.780 --> 00:38:48.780
Isn't love about giving your all?

00:38:49.260 --> 00:38:50.300
No holding back at all?

00:38:50.980 --> 00:38:52.420
It's Sen's first time being in love.

00:38:52.720 --> 00:38:54.100
I just don't want to see him get hurt.

00:38:56.800 --> 00:38:58.500
Even for a first love,
he has to hold back?

00:38:59.420 --> 00:39:01.620
Should we wait till
we're more experienced

00:39:01.620 --> 00:39:02.780
to go all in?

00:39:03.780 --> 00:39:05.060
Do you like eating cilantro?

00:39:05.420 --> 00:39:06.260
Mm?

00:39:07.140 --> 00:39:08.740
One day, Bei suddenly asked me that.

00:39:11.740 --> 00:39:13.540
Such a simple question.

00:39:14.150 --> 00:39:15.620
And I actually started overthinking it.

00:39:16.780 --> 00:39:17.780
I'm scared we'll find

00:39:17.780 --> 00:39:19.140
more and more differences between us.

00:39:21.340 --> 00:39:23.220
But honestly,
it doesn't matter if I like it.

00:39:24.260 --> 00:39:25.500
As long as he likes it,

00:39:26.580 --> 00:39:27.820
I'm willing to give it a try.

00:39:30.030 --> 00:39:32.020
Why does one person always
have to be the tolerant one?

00:39:33.600 --> 00:39:35.020
Isn't it better to just be yourself?

00:39:35.660 --> 00:39:37.540
But if you love someone,

00:39:37.940 --> 00:39:39.780
you want to
compromise and accommodate them.

00:39:40.080 --> 00:39:41.780
You start thinking about
them all the time.

00:39:44.660 --> 00:39:45.980
That's exactly how Bei is.

00:39:48.940 --> 00:39:50.020
Bei's right.

00:39:50.500 --> 00:39:52.340
It's never too late to
love someone you know.

00:39:55.100 --> 00:39:56.140
Seven years together.

00:39:56.140 --> 00:39:57.740
You must know each other pretty well.

00:39:59.100 --> 00:40:00.820
Mr. Bei, you're worrying too much.

00:40:01.020 --> 00:40:02.460
They're a perfect match.

00:40:02.660 --> 00:40:04.260
No need for a weirdo like you to object.

00:40:05.020 --> 00:40:07.020
And don't take yourself too seriously.

00:40:07.160 --> 00:40:08.460
I was just making a casual remark.

00:40:08.630 --> 00:40:09.540
Hey, Sen.

00:40:09.540 --> 00:40:11.340
Why don't you bring your girlfriend
to meet us?

00:40:11.340 --> 00:40:12.180
Come on.

00:40:12.200 --> 00:40:13.100
She'll be here a bit later.

00:40:13.100 --> 00:40:14.980
Did she get lost

00:40:14.980 --> 00:40:16.220
on the crowded path of love?

00:40:16.220 --> 00:40:17.340
You go pick her up?

00:40:17.340 --> 00:40:18.180
No need.

00:40:18.780 --> 00:40:20.180
She's taking her time to get ready.

00:40:21.900 --> 00:40:25.270
♪Waiting♪

00:40:26.910 --> 00:40:32.420
♪Waiting for the right time♪

00:40:34.610 --> 00:40:39.260
♪I'm just waiting♪

00:40:40.560 --> 00:40:44.660
♪Waiting for the right sign♪

00:40:52.120 --> 00:40:54.719
♪I'll admit♪

00:40:54.720 --> 00:40:58.759
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:40:59.640 --> 00:41:03.506
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

00:41:03.531 --> 00:41:07.719
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:41:08.000 --> 00:41:10.199
♪I'll resist♪

00:41:10.520 --> 00:41:12.534
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

00:41:12.559 --> 00:41:14.719
♪Your touches again♪

00:41:15.600 --> 00:41:19.580
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:41:19.605 --> 00:41:22.639
♪For an image of you♪

00:41:23.640 --> 00:41:26.079
♪Take my hand again♪

00:41:26.080 --> 00:41:27.839
♪Take my mind again♪

00:41:27.920 --> 00:41:31.279
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:41:31.680 --> 00:41:33.857
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:41:33.882 --> 00:41:35.719
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:41:35.720 --> 00:41:39.559
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:41:41.400 --> 00:41:45.559
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:41:45.560 --> 00:41:50.559
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:41:50.920 --> 00:41:53.879
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:41:53.960 --> 00:41:57.359
♪Did it come from above♪

00:41:57.440 --> 00:42:01.199
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:42:01.440 --> 00:42:06.519
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:42:06.920 --> 00:42:09.359
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:42:09.360 --> 00:42:13.799
♪This secret of love♪